data.description: Assumable VA Loan. Spacious four-bedroom townhome, featuring dual primary suites - one on each floor. End unit with 1,914 sq. ft. Downstairs boasts 9 ft. ceilings, tiled living area, a half bathroom, and a well-appointed kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, breakfast bar, and pantry. The downstairs primary bedroom has LVP flooring, walk-in closet, and the ensuite includes a double vanity with granite countertops and a shower and bathtub combo. The upstairs primary ensuite offers double vanity sinks, granite counters, separate shower, soaker bath tub, and water closet, along with a walk-in closet.Bedrooms 3 & 4 are located upstairs, along with the third full bathroom and laundry closet for convenience. LVP flooring in bedrooms, and wood tread on stairwell. Enjoy a large garage with ample storage space and a rear paved patio for BBQs. Located in Annabella's gated community off Hwy 98 in Panama City Beach, amenities include a swimming pool, clubhouse, and fitness center.Don't miss the chance to view this inviting home. Contact us to schedule a showing today!
